      • isExternal

        public boolean isExternal()
        Returns whether or not the server is an external server or was discovered on the local network.

        If the server is on the local network yet was added to the external server discovery list, this will yield true.

        Returns:
        true if the server is an external server, false if the server was discovered on the local network.
